data.title: January 2023 Transfers & News
data.meta_description: With the transfer window now closed, see all the deals from the winter window
data.text:
The January 2023 transfer window opened on 1 January and closed at 23:00 GMT on 31 January.

Find below all the signings and exits announced by Premier League clubs. All transfer fees are undisclosed unless otherwise stated.

(Last updated 2 February at 20:35 GMT)
